commitResults.messageTitle: Added Greet, Echo, Exit functionality to chatbot with formatting
Add the chatbot ability to store text input from the user and display them back to the user when requested
added Task class
Add chatbot functionality that allows users to mark tasks as done
Added Deadline class
Added Todo class and overrode toString() in Task class
Added Event class
Added support for tracking three types of tasks
Updated input.txt and EXPECTED.TXT for automated text ui testing
Added DukeException class
Added error handling for various incorrect user inputs
Updated automated ui testing to test error handling too
Changed storage for user tasks from Array to ArrayList
Added chatbot functionality to delete stored tasks
Added enums Commands to replace commonly used chatbox commands
Changed chatbot to close scanner after bye and removed some redundant function calls
Created test directory to store JUnit test classes and installed JUnit 5 dependency. Created dummy JUnit tests for Task class in TaskTest class.
Added unit tests for public members of Task class in TaskTest class
Improved code readability by creating new enums and abstracting some functions. Also updated EXPECTED.TXT to fit new changes.
Added methods to read and write to /data/dukeSave.txt file. Added /data/ to .gitignore so save files are not committed.
Implemented save and read functionality. Changes made to Task, Todo, Deadline and Event classes to facilitate converting Tasks to save format. .gitignore updated to ignore save files in text-ui-test.

Added functionality to parse LocalDate into formatted strings and to convert formatted strings into LocalDate. Deadline and Event objects now store LocalDate instead of any string. Added 2 new DukeException messages that corresponds to failure to parse LocalDate and failure to convert to LocalDate.
Fixed bug where empty task description is allowed for Event and Deadline in addTask() method.
